data.name: textBoxDescription.Text
data.value:
Half-Life Sound Magic
Made this because I was tired of the bug in HLSS, where you couldn't save binds with TAB. As with HLSS, hold Insert to play or press Delete to toggle playback.
As always, sounds should be 8000hz 16bit mono WAV files for HL, and 11025hz for Source. I suggest using the free program Audacity for convertion.
Contact: mads.lind@gmail.com
